Omega.exe.broken_*
Omega.exe.old_*
Omega.exe.pre_*.bak
Omega.exe.working_*
*.bak
*.bak_*
*.bak.20*
KILL_MICROSCALPER
KILL_MICROSCALPER.bak
omega_build.stamp
omega_config.ini.*.bak*
omega_config.ini.demo-bak-*
symbols.ini.*.bak*

